	<h1 class="title">要在美国这地界上卖卡车，日产先向三家公司致敬了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/26306/small/26306.jpg?1455710291" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">宣海伦 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-12 14:45:33 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20594/medium/20594.jpg?1452579159" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


